{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 945979, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 192118, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "疫情中期整天逼逼武汉实验室人造病毒的高中同学兼大学同学已经被我拉黑了", "timestamp": 1611202623, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 945981, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 192118, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "重点不是看他无脑相信什么，而是看他在你不相信的时候如何对待你，能不能跟你好好沟通吧。", "timestamp": 1611202662, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 945982, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 192118, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "提供一个可参考的案例", "timestamp": 1611202664, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 945983, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 192118, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "什么叫无脑相信，人总可以选择自己愿意相信的去相信，我还相信新冠是天罚呢。重点是，他是不是一个戾气重的人，如果是，那应该不止在这件事上是，那么，建议分手\n", "timestamp": 1611202689, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 945984, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 192118, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "可以跟他明确说一下他哪些说话方式 沟通态度让你感到不舒服之类的。", "timestamp": 1611202719, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 945986, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 192118, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "他相信是中国造的还是美国造的", "timestamp": 1611202747, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 945994, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 192118, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: Alice干得漂亮", "timestamp": 1611202878, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 945997, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 192118, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 觉得他相信阴谋论，容易被煽动，说不来", "timestamp": 1611202910, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 945998, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 192118, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 美国", "timestamp": 1611202924, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 946000, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 192118, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 无脑相信指外交部的发言被自媒体断章取义后他就兴奋了", "timestamp": 1611202963, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 946032, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 192118, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 那他很爱国嘛，往好处想啊", "timestamp": 1611203328, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 946061, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 192118, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "其实支持外交部发言的也有很多种立场\n1. 完全认同美国生化武器阴谋论\n2. 部分认同阴谋论，更多出于支持官方立场和反对美国\n3. 不认同阴谋论，但认为面对美国咄咄逼人只能不讲道理了\n4. 不关心，只是从大流\n\n我觉得dz再仔细辨明下吧。不同的立场对应不同的价值观，如果三观不合还是劝分吧", "timestamp": 1611203659, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 946109, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 192118, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "我向来是劝分不劝和的", "timestamp": 1611204172, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 946131, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 192118, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "其实这只是立场问题，与科学精神没有太大关系，能考上清华在理性方面都是过关的，只不过你npy的政治立场上大概比较红", "timestamp": 1611204459, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 946359, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 192118, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 唉但觉得很盲目", "timestamp": 1611206918, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 946361, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 192118, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 谢谢Eve", "timestamp": 1611206938, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 946363, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 192118, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Francis: 我也觉得", "timestamp": 1611206955, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 946365, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": tru